        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued September 15 at 3:48PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 348 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Lefors, or 13 miles southeast of Pampa, moving east at 5 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor hail damage to vegetation is
possible.

Locations impacted include...
Lefors.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
